title: BBQ & Picnic Area, Upgraded Units Available, Radiant Baseboard Heat
posting_body: ['Huntington House’s plush, landscaped courtyards with two community pools, walking paths, sundecks, barbecues and picnic tables welcomes residents with the perfect environment to call “home”.', 'Each apartment offers spacious floor plans, beautiful views of the courtyards and private entry.', 'Located on Fort Street enjoy Huntington House’s neighborhood charm in the city.', 'We would love for you to come on by and see what Huntington House has to offer!', '-Private Entrance', '-Late Fee Forgiveness', '-No Security Deposit Required', '-Online Payment Options (Credit Card, Debit Card and ACH)', '-Laundry Facility', '-One $35 Application Fee Per Apartment, Not Per Person', '-Upgraded Units Available', '-Additional Storage', '-BBQ & Picnic Area', '-Sparkling Clean Swimming Pool', '-Picture Windows with Courtyard Views', '-Air Conditioned', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability is subject to change.']
